<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.1">
<l>kōḻi yaḻaippataṉ muṉṉaṅ kuṭaintu nīrāṭuvāṉ pōntōm</l>
<l>āḻiyañ celva ṉeḻuntā ṉaravaṇai mēṟpaḷḷi koṇṭāy</l>
<l>ēḻai maiyāṟṟavum paṭṭō miṉiyeṉṟum poykaikku vārōm</l>
<l>tōḻiyu nāṉun toḻutōm tukilaip paṇittaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We set out for bathing, diving [in the pond], before the rooster crowed.</l>
<l>[Now] the beautiful [sun] lord has risen [as if] from the sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">O You who reclined upon the snake bed!</l>
<l>We have greatly suffered from helplessness. We will never come to the pond again!</l>
<l>My friends and I are praying to [You]: Do grace to give [back our] clothes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
